'''Sergei Viktorovich Savochkin''' ({{lang-ru|<U+0421><U+0435><U+0440><U+0433><U+0435><U+0439> <U+0412><U+0438><U+043A><U+0442><U+043E><U+0440><U+043E><U+0432><U+0438><U+0447> <U+0421><U+0430><U+0432><U+043E><U+0447><U+043A><U+0438><U+043D>}}; born February 8, 1976) is a [[Russia]]n professional [[Association football|footballer]]. As of April 2009, he plays for [[FC Mordovia Saransk]]. He made his debut in the [[Russian Premier League]] in 2004 for [[FC Amkar Perm]].

